data.description: OPEN HOUSE Saturday April 13th 12pm - 3pm. What a perfect time for you to be in the market for a new home. The search ends here! This home is centrally located on a quiet cul-de-sac in the heart of Pocatello. Come check out this charming 3 bedroom 1.5 bathroom home. There is also an additional bonus room and second living room for you to spread out and really enjoy the space. The garage adds convenience for those snowy Idaho winters when you won't have to scrape ice from your windshield. This beautiful home has a large backyard with a gorgeous gazebo perfect for relaxing and also includes a shed and a greenhouse for growing your own produce! Don't miss out on your chance to make this your new home! Buyer to verify home square footage.
